This paper deals with distributed online data mining and classification, which involves machine learning algorithms and big data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
